image/svg+xml\" sizes=\"any\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"bg-background text-foreground min-h-screen flex flex-col font-sans\"><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-[#f7f8fb] text-slate-950\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-[1480px] px-6 py-6 sm:px-10 xl:px-12\"><header class=\"flex justify-end rounded-[24px] border border-white/60 bg-white/70 px-5 py-3 backdrop-blur-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 transition hover:text-slate-900\" href=\"/?auth=login\">Log in</a><a class=\"rounded-xl bg-[#6f63dd] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#5e53cd]\" href=\"/?auth=signup\">Getting Started</a></div></header><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-2 py-10 sm:px-4 lg:py-14\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary\">Aura</p><h1 class=\"mt-3 text-4xl font-black tracking-[-0.04em] text-[#2e3277] sm:text-5xl\">Explore comunidades antes de entrar</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600\">Veja como a Aura organiza grupos por interesse, afinidade e contexto social sem exigir login logo no primeiro clique.</p></div><div class=\"mt-10\"><section id=\"communities\" class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-18\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-center\"><div class=\"max-w-xl\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary\">Comunidades</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-[-0.03em] text-slate-950 sm:text-4xl\">Conexão por interesse, não por caos.</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-slate-600\">Aura organiza a descoberta em torno de comunidades com contexto, afinidade e relevância social. Isso melhora tanto o feed quanto as conexões entre pessoas.</p><div class=\"mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Design</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">IA</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Produto</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Startups</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Web Dev</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Marketing</span></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4\"><div class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-[0_16px_48px_rgba(15,23,42,0.06)]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-950\">AI Builders</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Casos reais, testes práticos e discussões sobre IA aplicada ao trabalho.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600\">24 mil membros</div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-[0_16px_48px_rgba(15,23,42,0.06)]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-950\">Design Systems</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Escalabilidade, consistência visual e interfaces melhores para times de produto.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600\">13 mil membros</div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-[0_16px_48px_rgba(15,23,42,0.06)]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-950\">Growth Brasil</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Aquisição, retenção e loops de crescimento com foco em resultado de negócio.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600\">18 mil membros</div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#6f63dd] px-6 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#5e53cd]\" href=\"/?auth=signup\">Criar conta</a><a class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-[#d6def6] bg-white px-6 text-sm font-semibold text-[#40458a] transition hover:border-[#bfc9ef]\" href=\"/?auth=login\">Entrar</a></div></div></section></div></main><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-79efdc3d928800db.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[87424,[\\\"7984\\\",\\\"static/chunks/ef7830f0-774d581c3e223a57.js\\\",\\\"8960\\\",\\\"static/chunks/406b2ba4-1573ea644beca731.js\\\",\\\"7695\\\",\\\"static/chunks/7695-f386262b14f29a58.js\\\",\\\"5288\\\",\\\"static/chunks/5288-63462ff6f135c68a.js\\\",\\\"7177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-1c381122de0d0c90.js\\\"],\\\"ErrorBoundary\\\"]\\n3:I[32666,[\\\"7984\\\",\\\"static/chunks/ef7830f0-774d581c3e223a57.js\\\",\\\"8960\\\",\\\"static/chunks/406b2ba4-1573ea644beca731.js\\\",\\\"7695\\\",\\\"static/chunks/7695-f386262b14f29a58.js\\\",\\\"5288\\\",\\\"static/chunks/5288-63462ff6f135c68a.js\\\",\\\"7177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-1c381122de0d0c90.js\\\"],\\\"QueryProvider\\\"]\\n4:I[58197,[\\\"7984\\\",\\\"static/chunks/ef7830f0-774d581c3e223a57.js\\\",\\\"8960\\\",\\\"static/chunks/406b2ba4-1573ea644beca731.js\\\",\\\"7695\\\",\\\"static/chunks/7695-f386262b14f29a58.js\\\",\\\"5288\\\",\\\"static/chunks/5288-63462ff6f135c68a.js\\\",\\\"7177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-1c381122de0d0c90.js\\\"],\\\"AuthProvider\\\"]\\n5:I[93351,[\\\"7984\\\",\\\"static/chunks/ef7830f0-774d581c3e223a57.js\